constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Development up to 10 storeys to provide 194 dwellings; shopping, food and drink and professional services (Use Classes A1,A2 and A4); community, health, education and cultural uses (Use Class D1) and assembly and leisure uses (Class D2) together with provision of open space and landscaping; cycle ways and pedestrian routes; vehicle , motor cycle and cycle parking; provision and /or upgrading of infrastructure; groundworks and re-profiling of site levels and ancillary works. (AMENDED PROPOSAL INVOLVING THE DELETION OF ONE UNIT)
